The paper discusses the detection of phishing attacks, which is a common topic in the computer security (cs.CR) sub-category. The proposed approach involves implementing a web browser, which falls under the human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category. The paper also mentions the impact of phishing on online banking and e-commerce, which relates to the software engineering (cs.SE) and cyber security (cs.CY) sub-categories. Finally, the approach involves processing email data, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
